TEST authenticate_user_success

RECEIVE HTTP:GET /api/v1/users/auth
WITH {{payloads/auth_token_request.yaml}}

EXPECT READ:MYSQL users
USING_SQL """
SELECT * FROM `users` WHERE `users`.`token` = 'token_abc123xyz' LIMIT 1
"""
RETURNS {{payloads/user_response.json}}

RESPOND HTTP:200
WITH {{payloads/authenticated_user.yaml}}
